        <div class="content-body">
          <p>Choosing the right university is one of the most important decisions in a student's academic journey. At Grant Consulting, we take the time to understand your academic background, career aspirations, and personal preferences to match you with universities that truly fit your profile. With partnerships across more than 12 countries, we open doors to opportunities you might not discover on your own.</p>
          <p>Our experienced consultants evaluate universities based on program quality, global rankings, campus culture, location, and affordability. We compare options across multiple countries — including the United States, United Kingdom, Canada, Germany, South Korea, Malaysia, and beyond — so you can make an informed decision with a clear picture of what each institution offers.</p>
          <p>Every student receives a personalized shortlist of recommended universities along with a detailed admission assessment. We analyze your grades, test scores, and extracurricular achievements to identify where you have the strongest chance of acceptance, and we guide you through every step of the application process to maximize your results.</p>
        </div>

